TEXT.S: i Pingtung a kuwan nu Kalinku ku niyazu' nu Kabalelradhane. u kasalumaluma' nu Kabalelradhane sa, 130 ku luma'. kumud nu kasabinawlan sa, 405 ku tademawan. kasabinawlan nu Ingcumin sa, 399 ku tademaw, pakalatu 99%. u zuma sa, cay ku Ingcumin, 6 ku tademaw, pakalatu 1%. u kasabinacadan, Rukai 93%, Paiwan 4%, Amis 1%.
